<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-19-0785 </DOCNO><TEXT>A new toroidal magnet concept is presented, aimed at producing very large,quasistationary magnetic fields without the help of an external press.Such a high performance is obtained by tilting the winding's turns bya proper amount off the meridian plane, which results in a number offavourable consequences.</TEXT></DOC>